Value: Galena Mining Limited engages in the acquisition and exploration of mineral projects in Australia. It explores for copper, gold, lead, silver, zinc, and manganese deposits. The company owns a 100% interest in the Abra Base Metals lead-silver project located in the Gascoyne region, Western Australia. It also holds interests on Jillawarra prospects. Galena Mining Limited was incorporated in 2016 and is based in Subiaco, Australia.
